Oh well.

180
00:09:08,199 --> 00:09:10,375
They still love the Roses.

181
00:09:10,419 --> 00:09:12,247
I uploaded a video of
your performance

182
00:09:12,290 --> 00:09:15,511
and it already has 100,000 hits.

183
00:09:16,904 --> 00:09:17,905
Wow.

184
00:09:19,297 --> 00:09:20,777
Well, there ya go.

185
00:09:20,821 --> 00:09:21,822
And...

186
00:09:25,086 --> 00:09:26,740
This is what they're willing
to pay.

187
00:09:28,393 --> 00:09:29,394
Wow.

188
00:09:32,397 --> 00:09:33,485
Hmm.

189
00:09:33,529 --> 00:09:35,618
People want to see you again.

190
00:09:35,662 --> 00:09:38,099
They really are something
when they're on the same page.

191
00:09:38,142 --> 00:09:41,711
