me take care of business.

192
00:09:41,755 --> 00:09:44,584
More like micromanage my life.

193
00:09:44,627 --> 00:09:48,022
I just wanted you to share the
gifts God gave you.

194
00:09:48,065 --> 00:09:51,765
Not let them fall like pine
needles off a Christmas tree

195
00:09:51,808 --> 00:09:53,593
just because you made
a big mistake.

196
