265
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:11,070
We had such a good thing going
and she just,

266
00:13:11,094 --> 00:13:13,531
she left for some hair brained
idea that...

267
00:13:13,575 --> 00:13:14,619
Love.

268
00:13:15,490 --> 00:13:16,752
